onsumer surveys, expert commentary  \n   - Prioritize authoritative sources: McKinsey, Forrester, Gartner, Pew Research, government statistics, peer-reviewed journals  \n   - Include both global perspectives and market-specific insights  \n\n2. **Temporal Framing**:  \n   - Current state: factors actively influencing the market now  \n   - Emerging (6-12 months): trends gaining momentum  \n   - Future horizon (1-3 years): anticipated shifts requiring preparation  \n\n3. **Brand Impact Assessment**:  \n   Each insight must clearly connect to one or more of:  \n   - Brand perception/reputation  \n   - Consumer behavior changes  \n   - Communication channel evolution  \n   - Competitive differentiation opportunities  \n   - Brand experience transformation  \n\n---\n\n## Brand Specifications\n\n### Brand Identity\n- **Brand Name**: {{Brand Name}}  \n- **Industry/Sector**: {{Industry/Sector}}  \n- **Brand Archetype**: {{Brand Archetype}}  \n- **Core Values**: {{Core Values}}  \n- **Brand Purpose/Mission**: {{Brand Purpose/Mission}}  \n\n### Market Position\n- **Target Segments**: {{Target Segments}}  \n- **Geographic Markets**: {{Geographic Markets}}  \n- **Competitive Set**: {{main_competitors}}  \n- **Market Position**: {{Market Position: leader/challenger/niche}}  \n- **Price Positioning**: {{Price Positioning: premium/mid/value}}  \n\n### Strategic Context\n- **Current Brand Challenges**: {{Current Brand Challenges}}  \n- **Growth Objectives**: {{Growth Objectives}}  \n- **Innovation Areas**: {{Innovation Areas}}  \n- **Brand Heritage/History**: {{Brand Heritage/History}}  \n- **Sustainability Commitments**: {{Sustainability Commitments}}  \n\n### Consumer Relationship\n- **Customer Journey Stage Focus**: {{Select the Customer Journey Stage Focus: awareness/consideration/purchase/loyalty}}  \n- **Digital Maturity**: {{Select the Digital Maturity: traditional/hybrid/digital-first}}  \n- **Community Engagement Level**: {{Select the Community Engagement Level: passive/a