s sequentially\n  within each category (e.g., Political-1, Political-2, ..., Economic-1, Economic-2,\n  etc.).  \\n- Do not stop until you reach at least 20 insights in every category.  \\n-\n  Total output must therefore be between **120 and 450 insights** across all categories.  \\n\\n\\u003c\\u003cSEARCHER\\u003e\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\u003cPROMPT\\u003e\\u003e\n  \\nRetrieve all information about the {{client}} including its Product/Service, Mission/Vision,\n  Positioning, Target Audience, Unique Selling Proposition (USP), Competitors, Reference\n  Brands, Market Geography, Project/Goals Timeframe, and all insights related to Political,\n  Economic, Social, Technological, Legal, and Environmental factors that influence\n  brand strategy, perception, communications, trust, audience expectations, cultural\n  alignment, or social media relevance.\\n\\u003c\\u003cPROMPT\\u003e\\u003e\\n\\n\\u003c\\u003cPROMPT-GENERATOR\\u003e\\u003e\n  \\nRetrieve all information about the {{client}} including its Product/Service, Mission/Vision,\n  Positioning, Target Audience, Unique Selling Proposition (USP), Competitors, Reference\n  Brands, Market Geography, Project/Goals Timeframe, and all insights related to Political,\n  Economic, Social, Technological, Legal, and Environmental factors that influence\n  brand strategy, perception, communications, trust, audience expectations, cultural\n  alignment, or social media relevance.\\n\\u003c\\u003cPROMPT-GENERATOR\\u003e\\u003e\\n\\n\\n\\u003c\\u003cPROMPT\\u003e\\u003e\n  \\nSearch exclusively within the indexed knowledge base of generated **PESTLE Brand\n  Research Assignment** results.\\n\\n### Task:\\nRetrieve the **full set of exactly\n  120 insights (20 per category)** across the six PESTLE dimensions:\\n- Political\n  (P1–P20)  \\n- Economic (E1–E20)  \\n- Social (S1–S20)  \\n- Technological (T1–T20)  \\n-\n  Legal (L1–L20)  \\n- Environmental (EN1–EN20)  \\n\\u003c\\u003cPROMPT\\u003e\\u003e\\n\\n\\u003c\\u003cARTIFACT\\u003e\\u